img_build is used to pack a binary with boot header config.
It is used for boot2image and fw image. The final layout of
the image is as follows:

 /-------------------\
 |Boot_ Header_Config|   176 bytes
 |-------------------|
 |..... 0xFF.........|
 |......0xFF.........|
 |-------------------| offset
 |   src binary      |
 \-------------------/

The usage is:
$ ./img_gen -i boot_cfg_file -b src_bin -o output_bin -s offset
